    <h2>Who this is for</h2>
    <p>This page is for organisations that need reliable, coordinated lessons for the people they support. If you arrange lessons on behalf of others, we can help.</p>
    <ul class="feature-list" data-stagger>
      <li>Employment agencies arranging lessons for jobseekers.</li>
